<h2>Local SEO Is a Long-Term Asset</h2>
<p>Unlike Google Ads, which stop working the moment you stop paying, local SEO rankings compound over time. A business that has invested in local SEO for 12 months will generate leads for years, from a keyword they ranked for once.</p>
<p>The best time to start local SEO was when you launched your business. The second best time is today.</p>

<p>Local SEO applies across every Kenyan business sector. A <a href="/articles/medical-dental-website-kenya">dental clinic website Kenya</a> relies on local search to attract patients searching by neighbourhood and specialty. A <a href="/articles/restaurant-hotel-website-kenya">hotel website Kenya</a> needs to appear in "lodge near me" and destination-specific searches to reduce dependency on OTA commission.</p>

